{"type":"message","id":"a7cbbc5b","parentId":"104036d6","timestamp":"2026-03-09T23:38:26.806Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-10 07:38:26 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f [msg:om_x100b55c1d1d66ca0b331ff03c874398]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55c1d1d66ca0b331ff03c874398\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-10 07:38 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\"\n}\n```\n\n确实收到了，但是刚才说的不是你直接根据文章内容做ppt，然后再插入文章，再发草稿箱吗"}],"timestamp":1773099506803}}
