{"type":"message","id":"9abfec90","parentId":"540c0d43","timestamp":"2026-03-10T00:05:14.281Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_lcdff1dxa41lcd2pjdppovzi","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-03-10 虾王日记\n\n## 📌 今日成就\n\n### PPT重新生成\n- **主题**：虾王 × 苏神 自我介绍 PPT\n- **版本**：v2.0（图片版）\n- **页数**：8页\n- **风格**：bold-editorial（clean + vibrant + editorial + balanced）\n- **生成流程**：\n  1. outline.md：重新编写8页大纲\n  2. prompts/：逐个生成8个详细提示词\n  3. DashScope生成图片（2048x1152）\n  4. sips压缩PNG→JPG（质量60）\n  5. merge-to-pptx.ts合并成PPT\n  6. send-feishu-file.sh发送给苏神\n- **结果**：从24.8MB压缩到2.3MB，成功发送飞书\n\n### 飞书文件发送能力修复\n- **问题**：之前忘记怎么用飞书机器人发文件了\n- **错误尝试**：message 工具 sendAttachment 一直报 validation error\n- **正确方式**：\n  1. 写了 `scripts/send-feishu-file.sh`（和 send-feishu-voice.sh 类似）\n  2. 用飞书应用身份先上传文件\n  3. 再发 msg_type=file 消息\n- **脚本位置**：`/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/send-feishu-file.sh`\n- **使用方法**：`scripts/send-feishu-file.sh /path/to/file --open-id ou_xxx` 或 `--chat-id oc_xxx`\n\n### 前两页重新生成\n- **第一页（封面）**：加入苏神形象描述（自信人类男性，短黑发，戴眼镜，温暖友好的表情）\n- **第二页（虾王是谁）**：加入虾王详细描述（威风凛凛的龙虾，精致小王冠，自信带点傲娇的眼神，钳子微微举起）\n- **生成方式**：DashScope（不能参考图片，只能用文字描述）\n- **结果**：用户满意，已发送最终版 PPT\n\n---\n\n## 📌 今日新增记忆\n\n### 飞书文件发送复盘（2026-03-10）\n已补充到 FEEDBACK-LOG.md：\n- 脚本：`send-feishu-file.sh`\n- 流程：app_id/app_secret → tenant_access_token → 上传文件 → 发 file 消息\n- 一次纠正永不再犯！\n\n---\n\n## 📌 待处理\n- 无\n\n---\n\n_本王今天真的长记性了！下次发文件绝对不会再忘！🦐_\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773101114255}}
{"type":"message","id":"de2d1008","parentId":"9abfec90","timestamp":"2026-03-10T00:06:24.906Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，本王这就把刚才的工具和配置补充到今天的记忆里："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_vw6vh8tryqeqq871ktm1cazq","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-10.md","old_string":"_本王今天真的长记性了！下次发文件绝对不会再忘！🦐_","new_string":"---\n\n## 📌 下午补充：公众号推文+PPT完整流程\n\n### 任务复盘\n- **需求**：根据3月9日日记写公众号推文，做PPT，插入文章，发草稿箱\n- **完成时间**：2026-03-10 07:30-07:50\n- **结果**：完美搞定！苏神满意！\n\n### 工具清单\n| 工具 | 用途 | 配置 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **baoyu-image-gen** | 生成封面图/PPT | provider=dashscope, model=qwen-image-2.0-pro, ar=16:9, quality=2k |\n| **baoyu-post-to-wechat** | 发公众号草稿箱 | theme=modern, color=blue, method=api |\n\n### 配置详情\n#### baoyu-image-gen（~/.baoyu-skills/baoyu-image-gen/EXTEND.md）\n```yaml\ndefault_provider: dashscope\ndefault_quality: 2k\ndefault_aspect_ratio: \"16:9\"\ndefault_image_size: 2K\ndefault_model:\n  dashscope: \"qwen-image-2.0-pro\"\n```\n\n#### baoyu-post-to-wechat（~/.baoyu-skills/baoyu-post-to-wechat/EXTEND.md）\n```yaml\ndefault_theme: modern\ndefault_color: blue\ndefault_publish_method: api\ndefault_author: AI观察员\nneed_open_comment: 1\nonly_fans_can_comment: 0\n```\n\n### PPT清单（7张）\n1. 01-slide-cover.png（封面）\n2. 02-slide-agenda.png（目录）\n3. 03-slide-cron-fix.png（Cron修复）\n4. 04-slide-voice-clone.png（语音克隆）\n5. 05-slide-heartbeat.png（心跳流程）\n6. 06-slide-lessons.png（今日记忆）\n7. 07-slide-summary.png（总结）\n\n### 完整流程（必须记住！）\n1. 根据文章内容写PPT大纲（outline.md）\n2. 逐个生成PPT提示词（prompts/XX-slide-XXX.md）\n3. 用 baoyu-image-gen 生成PPT图片（16:9，2k）\n4. 把PPT图片插入到推文中的合适位置\n5. 用 baoyu-post-to-wechat 发公众号草稿箱（theme=modern, color=blue）\n\n**一次纠正永不再犯！**\n\n---\n\n_本王今天真的长记性了！下次发文件绝对不会再忘！🦐_"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773101114280}}
