{"type":"message","id":"084310ff","parentId":"a307e540","timestamp":"2026-03-10T05:28:05.834Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，还是限流——没关系，苏神你有浏览器的话，可以直接访问 https://clawhub.ai/iswalle/getnote 然后把技能的文件下载下来，或者直接把技能的内容复制给本王！\n\n或者苏神你可以等一会儿（大概1分钟），等限流恢复了，本王再试 clawhub 命令！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773120479123}}
