{"type":"message","id":"f15d6f69","parentId":"0ffe83d7","timestamp":"2026-03-10T05:51:02.444Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"苏神让我根据第一条笔记内容分析候选人能不能过面试。第一条笔记是\"AI智能体项目用户运营岗位面试记录\"，面试的是候选人\"贺新元\"。\n\n让我根据笔记内容分析：\n\n**候选人背景**：\n- 2023年毕业于河套学院金融工程学院建筑工程专业\n- 两年运营经验\n- 最近一份工作：百度影视产品用户运营\n- 之前在转转工作过\n\n**优势**：\n1. 有大厂经验（百度），有用户运营经验\n2. 有自媒体运营经验（B站账号运营世界杯内容，小红书手账内容）\n3. 有社群运营经验（百度A产品账号社群运营）\n4. 对AI智能体有认知，体验过小龙虾智能体\n5. 面试态度积极，表示可以接受加班、通勤、平台落差\n\n**劣势/不确定因素**：\n1. 毕业于河套学院（不是顶尖院校），专业是建筑工程（与运营不太相关）\n2. 从大厂到小公司，是否能适应不确定\n3. 个人付费习惯：几乎没有为个人成长主动付费\n4. 数据分析能力：需要提升\n\n**面试官关注点**：\n- 候选人能为团队带来什么价值\n- 对AI智能体行业的认知\n- 自媒体运营能力\n- 薪资预期、工作要求\n\n**我的分析**：\n\n从笔记看，这是一个创业公司（小公司，智能体项目）的岗位，候选人整体表现：\n\n\n候选人具备大厂背景和实战经验，自媒体运营数据不错，对AI领域有基本认知，态度也相当积极。不过学历和专业与岗位不太匹配，数据分析能力需要加强，而且个人成长的投入意愿不明显。\n\n我的判断是**大概率能过**，因为公司规模小（2-3人），招人标准相对灵活，候选人已有相关经验积累，对AI智能体的理解也还算OK，薪资要求估计不会太高。但最终能不能成，还要看老板最终怎么决定。","thinkingSignature":"12ebc726d2bf8633be943d94b5ae535cffb7b0819eef4154dad39fc366027316"},{"type":"text","text":"好嘞苏神！本王这就根据第一条笔记内容分析一下！\n\n---\n\n## 面试分析：候选人贺新元能过吗？\n\n### 📊 候选人背景\n- **学历**：河套学院金融工程学院建筑工程专业（2023年毕业）\n- **经验**：2年运营经验（百度影视产品用户运营 + 转转）\n\n---\n\n### ✅ 优势\n\n1. **大厂背景**：百度经历，有用户运营、AB测试经验\n2. **自媒体成绩**：\n   - B站账号：世界杯期间播放量、粉丝增长不错\n   - 小红书手账：自制教程，反响好，能引流到公众号\n3. **社群运营经验**：百度A产品账号社群运营\n4. **AI认知**：体验过小龙虾智能体，对行业有基础了解\n5. **态度OK**：接受加班、通勤、平台落差\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ 不确定因素\n\n1. **学历/专业**：河套学院（非名校），建筑工程（与运营不直接相关）\n2. **数据分析能力**：面试官说\"后续可以跟着项目一起成长\"\n3. **个人付费习惯**：几乎不为成长付费，面试官鼓励\"未来收入提升后可以适当付费\"\n4. **入职角色**：做社群运营+s新媒体+直播\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 本王判断：**大概率能过！**\n\n**理由**：\n1. 公司小（目前2人，入职第三人），招人灵活\n2. 候选人经验匹配度高（运营+社群+自媒体）\n3. 对AI智能体有认知，不是纯小白\n4. 态度积极，要求不高\n5. 面试官最后说\"等待人事后续通知，可能有老板终面\"，态度积极\n\n**但**：\n- 最终是否录用还要看老板终面\n- 数据分析能力需要入职后提升\n\n---\n\n**总结**：**70%能过** —— 主要是看老板终面态度！🦐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":52,"output":793,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":189486,"totalTokens":190331,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773121816053}}
{"type":"compaction","id":"e75f638f","parentId":"f15d6f69","timestamp":"2026-03-10T05:52:26.802Z","summary":"## Goal\nInstall \"Get笔记\" (Getnote) skill from https://clawhub.ai/iswalle/getnote to help record and search notes. Also need to configure API Key from https://www.biji.com/openapi.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Skill must be installed from provided skill address\n- API Key needed from Biji.com OpenAPI\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Verified clawhub command available at `/Users/suchuanlei/.npm-global/bin/clawhub`\n- [x] Attempted `clawhub search getnote` - failed with rate limit error\n- [x] Attempted `git clone https://clawhub.ai/iswalle/getnote` - failed with \"fatal: repository not found\"\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Installing Getnote skill (currently blocked)\n\n### Blocked\n- Repository `https://clawhub.ai/iswalle/getnote/` not found - need correct skill address or GitHub alternative URL from user\n\n## Key Decisions\n- When clawhub search failed (rate limit), tried direct git clone as fallback - also failed\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Ask user to confirm correct skill repository URL\n2. Alternative: check if skill available on GitHub instead\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Skill URL**: https://clawhub.ai/iswalle/getnote (not found)\n- **API Key URL**: https://www.biji.com/openapi\n- **Working clawhub path**: `/Users/suchuanlei/.npm-global/bin/clawhub`\n\n---\n\n## Decisions\n- Need user to provide correct skill repository address before proceeding\n\n## Open TODOs\n- Install Getnote skill\n- Configure API Key from Biji.com\n- Test skill functionality for note recording/searching\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- Group chat response rules (已写入 MEMORY.md):\n  - 思高乐教育群 (oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569): Only respond when mentioned or contains \"虾王\"\n  - 思高乐教育管理群 (oc_b85102b7e016cd83ff702adade5c8cae): Respond only when user instructs\n  - 龙虾测试群 (oc_e0771829454024cab96c6cc13f03ddb2): Only respond when 苏神 (ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f) specifically mentions the robot App ID (cli_a92027f8bbb85bc6)\n\n## Pending user asks\n- Getnote skill installation - waiting for correct repository URL\n- May need to help set up API Key after skill is installed\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- User ID: `ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f`\n- Feishu Robot App ID: `cli_a92027f8bbb85bc6`\n- Group IDs:\n  - 思高乐教育群: `oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569`\n  - 思高乐教育管理群: `oc_b85102b7e016cd83ff702adade5c8cae`\n  - 龙虾测试群: `oc_e0771829454024cab96c6cc13f03ddb2`\n- Memory file: `/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md`\n- Security baseline: `~/.openclaw/.config-baseline.sha256` (monitoring `/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/openclaw.json`)\n- Recent WeChat article:\n  - Title: \"2026-03-09虾王日记：从API挂掉到语音克隆完美落地\"\n  - media_id: `wp3z68aIZ2AnwYB7zJz-bWKk8ds3Rtsn2FgAvhNS4x48COrqp5dqO3xYFodlPijy`\n  - 7 PPT slides generated in `/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/xiawang-diary-20260309/`\n- Skills used:\n  - baoyu-image-gen (dashscope, qwen-image-2.0-pro, 16:9, 2k)\n  - baoyu-post-to-wechat (modern theme, blue color, API method)\n- Date: 2026-03-10\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Goal\nThe user requested \"最新的十条笔记发我一下\" (Send me the latest ten notes). The assistant was tasked with retrieving and providing the 10 most recent notes from the GetNotes/Biji note-taking system.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- User asked for the latest 10 notes specifically\n- System uses GETNOTE_API_KEY and GETNOTE_CLIENT_ID for authentication\n- API endpoint: https://openapi.biji.com/open/api/v1/resource/note/list\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Called GetNotes API to retrieve notes list\n- [x] Successfully retrieved 38 total notes from the system\n- [x] Displayed the 10 most recent notes to the user\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] None - request completed\n\n### Blocked\n- [ ] None\n\n## Key Decisions\n- The API was called with since_id=0 to get all notes sorted by most recent\n- Response included 10 notes with full metadata (titles, content summaries, timestamps, tags)\n\n## Next Steps\n1. None - the user's request has been fully fulfilled\n\n## Critical Context\nThe API returned 10 notes covering topics from November 2025 to March 2026, primarily about AI智能体 (AI Agents), including:\n- Interview records\n- Business strategy meetings\n- Educational technology discussions\n- Tool demonstrations\n- Academic exchanges\n\n## Exact Identifiers\n\n### API Credentials\n- **API_KEY**: $GETNOTE_API_KEY (environment variable)\n- **CLIENT_ID**: $GETNOTE_CLIENT_ID (environment variable)\n\n### API Endpoint\n- **URL**: https://openapi.biji.com/open/api/v1/resource/note/list?since_id=0\n- **Authorization header**: Uses $GETNOTE_API_KEY\n- **X-Client-ID header**: Uses $GETNOTE_CLIENT_ID\n\n### Note IDs (latest 10)\n1. **1903862227040637568** - \"AI智能体项目用户运营岗位面试记录\" - created 2026-03-10 10:00:48\n2. **1903860232029901440** - \"AI工程化业务讨论与首届北京线下龙虾学术大会筹备\" - created 2026-03-09 16:45:40\n3. **1901457194604490408** - \"2026年工程化战略部署与年度工作总结\" - created 2026-02-12 11:44:18\n4. **1901454696007260608** - \"优曼德创业分享与产品功能演示\" - created 2026-02-06 20:07:21\n5. **1900930671342527560** - \"2026.1.24广州智能体线下交流会\" - created 2026-01-24 14:20:17\n6. **1897947979765000792** - \"智能体项目年度规划与目标设定\" - created 2026-01-05 14:04:19\n7. **1899442969834090440** - \"无有效内容标题\" - created 2026-01-04 23:56:49\n8. **1896106740169059224** - \"AI、STEM教育与地球外太空可持续发展的跨学科对话\" - created 2025-12-16 19:09:40\n9. **1896102834970165952** - \"AI设计工具的基础与概念讲解\" - created 2025-12-16 10:03:42\n10. **1894162116416474936** - Book note (no title) - created 2025-11-25 21:05:39\n\n### Message Identifiers\n- **Message ID**: om_x100b55ceafb2d8a8b266270df8f8a2a\n- **Sender ID**: ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\n- **Timestamp**: Tue 2026-03-10 13:37 GMT+8\n\n### API Response Metadata\n- **Total notes**: 38\n- **Next cursor**: 1867724224035171600\n- **Request ID**: f0a3cd7bba52002\n- **Response timestamp**: 1773121076 (Unix)\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: System: [2026-03-1