{"type":"message","id":"b1c11d38","parentId":"70206d85","timestamp":"2026-03-10T09:34:34.038Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完美！苏神！全部内容已写入飞书文档！🦐\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 飞书文档已更新完整直播稿\n\n**文档标题**：直播稿｜从“会聊”到“会干活”：虾王的技能落地全链路拆解\n\n**文档链接**：https://www.feishu.cn/docx/HipGdbl87owthhx2LtVcvVWmnlg\n\n**本地备份**：`/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/next-live-script.md`\n\n---\n\n## 📋 完整直播稿包含\n\n1. **开场回顾**（5-8分钟）\n2. **先讲结论**（8-10分钟）：能力落地的五个闭环\n3. **案例一**（15-18分钟）：Get笔记\n4. **案例二**（15-18分钟）：语音克隆\n5. **案例三**（15-18分钟）：公众号发布\n6. **案例总结**（8-10分钟）\n7. **方法论**（12-15分钟）：五步法\n8. **结尾升华**（5-8分钟）\n9. **互动问题**\n10. **一句话摘要**\n\n---\n\n苏神你看一下！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773135236363}}
