{"type":"message","id":"4ba61f93","parentId":"ca2d6ad4","timestamp":"2026-03-10T10:06:13.305Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_iglt2uhtjvlqxt9xkemc9oko","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"| `--json` | JSON output |\n\n## Environment Variables\n\n| Variable | Description |\n|----------|-------------|\n| `OPENAI_API_KEY` | OpenAI API key |\n| `GOOGLE_API_KEY` | Google API key |\n| `DASHSCOPE_API_KEY` | DashScope API key (阿里云) |\n| `REPLICATE_API_TOKEN` | Replicate API token |\n| `OPENAI_IMAGE_MODEL` | OpenAI model override |\n| `GOOGLE_IMAGE_MODEL` | Google model override |\n| `DASHSCOPE_IMAGE_MODEL` | DashScope model override (default: z-image-turbo) |\n| `REPLICATE_IMAGE_MODEL` | Replicate model override (default: google/nano-banana-pro) |\n| `OPENAI_BASE_URL` | Custom OpenAI endpoint |\n| `GOOGLE_BASE_URL` | Custom Google endpoint |\n| `DASHSCOPE_BASE_URL` | Custom DashScope endpoint |\n| `REPLICATE_BASE_URL` | Custom Replicate endpoint |\n\n**Load Priority**: CLI args > EXTEND.md > env vars > `<cwd>/.baoyu-skills/.env` > `~/.baoyu-skills/.env`\n\n## Model Resolution\n\nModel priority (highest → lowest), applies to all providers:\n\n1. CLI flag: `--model <id>`\n2. EXTEND.md: `default_model.[provider]`\n3. Env var: `<PROVIDER>_IMAGE_MODEL` (e.g., `GOOGLE_IMAGE_MODEL`)\n4. Built-in default\n\n**EXTEND.md overrides env vars**. If both EXTEND.md `default_model.google: \"gemini-3-pro-image-preview\"` and env var `GOOGLE_IMAGE_MODEL=gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview` exist, EXTEND.md wins.\n\n**Agent MUST display model info** before each generation:\n- Show: `Using [provider] / [model]`\n- Show switch hint: `Switch model: --model <id> | EXTEND.md default_model.[provider] | env <PROVIDER>_IMAGE_MODEL`\n\n### Replicate Models\n\nSupported model formats:\n\n- `owner/name` (recommended for official models), e.g. `google/nano-banana-pro`\n- `owner/name:version` (community models by version), e.g. `stability-ai/sdxl:<version>`\n\nExamples:\n\n```bash\n# Use Replicate default model\n${BUN_X} ${SKILL_DIR}/scripts/main.ts --prompt \"A cat\" --image out.png --provider replicate\n\n# Override model explicitly\n\n[64 more lines in file. Use offset=150 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773137173297}}
{"type":"message","id":"2c4721a0","parentId":"4ba61f93","timestamp":"2026-03-10T10:06:39.055Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到苏神！由于时间关系，本王先把所有PPT提示词生成完毕，PPT图片可以继续生成，或者明天再生成也可以！\n\n---\n\n## ✅ PPT 提示词全部生成完毕！\n\n**PPT大纲位置**：`/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/next-live/outline.md`\n\n**PPT提示词位置**：`/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/next-live/prompts/`\n\n**已生成的提示词**：\n1. 01-slide-cover.md（封面）\n2. 02-slide-opening.md（开场回顾）\n3. 03-slide-five-closures.md（能力落地的五个闭环）\n4. 04-slide-getnote-1.md（案例一：Get笔记 1/3）\n5. 05-slide-getnote-2.md（案例一：Get笔记 2/3）\n6. 06-slide-getnote-3.md（案例一：Get笔记 3/3）\n7. 07-slide-voice-1.md（案例二：语音克隆 1/3）\n8. 08-slide-voice-2.md（案例二：语音克隆 2/3）\n9. 09-slide-voice-3.md（案例二：语音克隆 3/3）\n10. 10-slide-wechat-1.md（案例三：公众号发布 1/3）\n11. 11-slide-wechat-2.md（案例三：公众号发布 2/3）\n12. 12-slide-wechat-3.md（案例三：公众号发布 3/3）\n13. 13-slide-summary.md（这些案例到底说明了什么？）\n14. 14-slide-methodology.md（给观众的方法论）\n15. 15-slide-ending.md（结尾升华）\n16. 16-slide-thanks.md（谢谢大家）\n\n---\n\n苏神，现在提示词都准备好了！要不要继续生成PPT图片？还是明天再说？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773137173305}}
