{"type":"message","id":"ee8afb87","parentId":"0077df22","timestamp":"2026-03-10T11:09:17.829Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完美！苏神！全部16张PPT生成成功！🦐🎉\n\n---\n\n## ✅ PPT全部生成完毕！（16/16）\n\n**位置**：`/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/next-live/images/`\n\n**已生成的PPT**：\n1. ✅ 01-slide-cover.png（封面）\n2. ✅ 02-slide-opening.png（开场回顾）\n3. ✅ 03-slide-five-closures.png（能力落地的五个闭环）\n4. ✅ 04-slide-getnote-1.png（案例一：Get笔记 1/3）\n5. ✅ 05-slide-getnote-2.png（案例一：Get笔记 2/3）\n6. ✅ 06-slide-getnote-3.png（案例一：Get笔记 3/3）\n7. ✅ 07-slide-voice-1.png（案例二：语音克隆 1/3）\n8. ✅ 08-slide-voice-2.png（案例二：语音克隆 2/3）\n9. ✅ 09-slide-voice-3.png（案例二：语音克隆 3/3）\n10. ✅ 10-slide-wechat-1.png（案例三：公众号发布 1/3）\n11. ✅ 11-slide-wechat-2.png（案例三：公众号发布 2/3）\n12. ✅ 12-slide-wechat-3.png（案例三：公众号发布 3/3）\n13. ✅ 13-slide-summary.png（这些案例到底说明了什么？）\n14. ✅ 14-slide-methodology.png（给观众的方法论）\n15. ✅ 15-slide-ending.png（结尾升华）\n16. ✅ 16-slide-thanks.png（谢谢大家）\n\n---\n\n## 📦 完整交付\n\n1. ✅ 飞书文档：https://www.feishu.cn/docx/HipGdbl87owthhx2LtVcvVWmnlg\n2. ✅ PPT大纲：`/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/next-live/outline.md`\n3. ✅ 所有PPT提示词：`/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/next-live/prompts/`\n4. ✅ 全部16张PPT图片：`/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/next-live/images/`\n\n---\n\n苏神下班愉快！明天见！🦐✨"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773140931545}}
