{"type":"message","id":"ad71098d","parentId":"4934237b","timestamp":"2026-03-10T11:39:59.243Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到苏神！本王这就给你详细说 baoyu-image-gen 的 API 配置！\n\n---\n\n## 📋 baoyu-image-gen API 配置说明\n\n### 🔑 环境变量配置方式（推荐）\n\n在你的 shell 配置文件（`~/.zshrc` 或 `~/.bashrc`）中添加：\n\n```bash\n# DashScope (阿里云通义万象) - 当前在用的\nexport DASHSCOPE_API_KEY=\"你的dashscope-api-key\"\n\n# Google (Gemini) - 可选\nexport GOOGLE_API_KEY=\"你的google-api-key\"\n\n# OpenAI (DALL-E) - 可选\nexport OPENAI_API_KEY=\"你的openai-api-key\"\n\n# Replicate - 可选\nexport REPLICATE_API_TOKEN=\"你的replicate-api-token\"\n```\n\n配置后执行：`source ~/.zshrc`\n\n---\n\n### 📄 偏好配置文件（已配置）\n\n**位置**：`~/.baoyu-skills/baoyu-image-gen/EXTEND.md`\n\n**当前配置**：\n```yaml\nversion: 1\n\ndefault_provider: dashscope\ndefault_quality: 2k\ndefault_aspect_ratio: \"16:9\"\ndefault_image_size: 2K\ndefault_model:\n  dashscope: \"qwen-image-2.0-pro\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 支持的提供商和模型\n\n| 提供商 | 模型 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| **dashscope** (默认) | `qwen-image-2.0-pro` | 阿里云通义万象 |\n| **google** | `gemini-3-pro-image-preview` | Google Gemini |\n| **openai** | `gpt-image-1.5` | OpenAI DALL-E |\n| **replicate** | `google/nano-banana-pro` | Replicate 模型 |\n\n---\n\n### 💡 常用使用方式\n\n```bash\n# 使用默认配置（DashScope，16:9，2k）\nbun ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-image-gen/scripts/main.ts \\\n  --prompt \"提示词\" \\\n  --image output.png\n\n# 指定提供商和模型\nbun ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-image-gen/scripts/main.ts \\\n  --prompt \"提示词\" \\\n  --image output.png \\\n  --provider google \\\n  --model gemini-3-pro-image-preview\n\n# 从文件读取提示词\nbun ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-image-gen/scripts/main.ts \\\n  --promptfiles prompt1.md prompt2.md \\\n  --image output.png\n```\n\n---\n\n苏神你看还需要配置什么吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"