{"type":"message","id":"13f23362","parentId":"1458c0aa","timestamp":"2026-03-10T11:43:48.848Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_m9wopytb69d7g312jhr34su2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Collect results via TaskOutput when all complete\n```\n\n## Error Handling\n\n- Missing API key → error with setup instructions\n- Generation failure → auto-retry once\n- Invalid aspect ratio → warning, proceed with default\n- Reference images with unsupported provider/model → error with fix hint (switch to Google multimodal: `gemini-3-pro-image-preview`, `gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview`; or OpenAI GPT Image edits)\n\n## Extension Support\n\nCustom configurations via EXTEND.md. See **Preferences** section for paths and supported options.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773143028839}}
{"type":"message","id":"31c5f552","parentId":"13f23362","timestamp":"2026-03-10T11:44:13.585Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到苏神！本王这就给你说 Replicate 需要的参数！\n\n---\n\n## 📋 Replicate 参数说明\n\n### 🔑 必须参数\n\n1. **环境变量**（必须配置）\n   ```bash\n   export REPLICATE_API_TOKEN=\"你的replicate-api-token\"\n   ```\n\n2. **命令行参数**（必须提供）\n   - `--provider replicate`：指定使用 Replicate\n   - `--prompt <text>` 或 `--promptfiles <files>`：提示词\n   - `--image <path>`：输出图片路径\n\n---\n\n### 📌 可选参数\n\n| 参数 | 说明 | 默认值 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| `--model <owner/name>` | Replicate 模型 | `google/nano-banana-pro` |\n| `--ar <ratio>` | 宽高比（16:9/1:1/4:3等） | 从 EXTEND.md 读取 |\n| `--quality <normal\\|2k>` | 质量预设 | 从 EXTEND.md 读取 |\n| `--n <count>` | 生成图片数量 | 1 |\n\n---\n\n### 💡 使用示例\n\n```bash\n# 基本用法（默认模型 google/nano-banana-pro）\nbun ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-image-gen/scripts/main.ts \\\n  --provider replicate \\\n  --prompt \"一只可爱的龙虾\" \\\n  --image output.png\n\n# 指定模型\nbun ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-image-gen/scripts/main.ts \\\n  --provider replicate \\\n  --model stability-ai/sdxl \\\n  --prompt \"一只可爱的龙虾\" \\\n  --image output.png\n\n# 指定宽高比和质量\nbun ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-image-gen/scripts/main.ts \\\n  --provider replicate \\\n  --prompt \"一只可爱的龙虾\" \\\n  --image output.png \\\n  --ar 16:9 \\\n  --quality 2k\n```\n\n---\n\n### 📦 支持的模型格式\n\n- `owner/name`（推荐）：`google/nano-banana-pro`\n- `owner/name:version`：`stability-ai/sdxl:v1`\n\n---\n\n苏神你看还需要什么细节吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773143028848}}
