{"type":"message","id":"2e3ff7b9","parentId":"faa948a1","timestamp":"2026-03-10T11:48:08.953Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到苏神！本王这就给你说 Google 的配置！\n\n---\n\n## 📋 Google 配置说明\n\n### 🔑 必须配置\n```bash\nexport GOOGLE_API_KEY=\"你的google-api-key\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🌐 Base URL 配置\n\n### ✅ 默认就可以，不需要改\n- 默认 Base URL：`https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com`\n- **不需要**额外配置 `GOOGLE_BASE_URL`\n\n### 🔧 非要改也可以（不推荐）\n如果需要自定义 Base URL：\n```bash\nexport GOOGLE_BASE_URL=\"你的自定义url\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 💡 最简单的用法\n\n```bash\n# 1. 只配置 API Key\nexport GOOGLE_API_KEY=\"AIza...\"\n\n# 2. 直接用\nbun ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-image-gen/scripts/main.ts \\\n  --provider google \\\n  --prompt \"一只可爱的龙虾\" \\\n  --image output.png\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📊 支持的 Google 模型\n\n| 模型 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `gemini-3-pro-image-preview` | 高级图像生成 |\n| `gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview` | 快速图像生成 |\n\n---\n\n就这么简单！默认 Base URL 就够了！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773143262875}}
