{"type":"message","id":"5a264d28","parentId":"86cd2f13","timestamp":"2026-03-10T12:56:09.119Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到苏神！压缩包太大飞书发不出去！没关系，本王告诉你位置，你直接在本地打开！\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 两个版本的PPT压缩包已打好！\n\n### 📦 DashScope 版\n**位置**：`/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/next-live/dashscope-ppt.zip`\n**内容**：16张PPT图片\n\n### 📦 Google 版\n**位置**：`/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/next-live/google-ppt.zip`\n**内容**：16张PPT图片\n\n---\n\n或者直接打开文件夹看原图：\n- **DashScope 版原图**：`/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/next-live/images/`\n- **Google 版原图**：`/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/next-live/images-google/`\n\n---\n\n苏神你直接在本地打开文件夹看就行！🦐✨"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773147347411}}
