{"type":"message","id":"b47d3065","parentId":"3146c807","timestamp":"2026-03-10T13:50:22.639Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking what skill I used to generate the PPT, and whether I can use baoyu-slide-deck to generate another version.\n\nLet me answer:\n1. I used baoyu-image-gen to generate the images, then used python-pptx to combine them into a .pptx file\n2. I can try baoyu-slide-deck skill to generate another version\n\nLet me first check if baoyu-slide-deck skill is available and how to use it.","thinkingSignature":"a719bc5e67e29e212717f530328da4f7ffcdb760aa389970deeb84b157a4077b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n收到苏神！本王回答你：\n\n---\n\n## 📋 这次用的技能\n\n1. **baoyu-image-gen**：生成16张PPT图片（用 Google/gemini-3-pro-image-preview 模型）\n2. **python-pptx**（Python库）：把16张图片合并成 .pptx 文件\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 能不能用 baoyu-slide-deck 生成？\n\n当然可以！本王来看看 baoyu-slide-deck 怎么用！\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_iqjmcmgp4ncx_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-slide-deck/SKILL.md","limit":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":52,"output":258,"cacheRead":170165,"cacheWrite":3266,"totalTokens":173741,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773150610199}}
{"type":"message","id":"726febd1","parentId":"b47d3065","timestamp":"2026-03-10T13:50:22.660Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_iqjmcmgp4ncx_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: baoyu-slide-deck\ndescription: Generates professional slide deck images from content. Creates outlines with style instructions, then generates individual slide images. Use when user asks to \"create slides\", \"make a presentation\", \"generate deck\", \"slide deck\", or \"PPT\".\n---\n\n# Slide Deck Generator\n\nTransform content into professional slide deck images.\n\n## Usage\n\n```bash\n/baoyu-slide-deck path/to/content.md\n/baoyu-slide-deck path/to/content.md --style sketch-notes\n/baoyu-slide-deck path/to/content.md --audience executives\n/baoyu-slide-deck path/to/content.md --lang zh\n/baoyu-slide-deck path/to/content.md --slides 10\n/baoyu-slide-deck path/to/content.md --outline-only\n/baoyu-slide-deck  # Then paste content\n```\n\n## Script Directory\n\n**Agent Execution Instructions**:\n1. Determine this SKILL.md file's directory path as `SKILL_DIR`\n2. Script path = `${SKILL_DIR}/scripts/<script-name>.ts`\n3. Resolve `${BUN_X}` runtime: if `bun` installed → `bun`; if `npx` available → `npx -y bun`; else suggest installing bun\n\n| Script | Purpose |\n|--------|---------|\n| `scripts/merge-to-pptx.ts` | Merge slides into PowerPoint |\n| `scripts/merge-to-pdf.ts` | Merge slides into PDF |\n\n## Options\n\n| Option | Description |\n|--------|-------------|\n| `--style <name>` | Visual style: preset name, `custom`, or custom style name |\n| `--audience <type>` | Target: beginners, intermediate, experts, executives, general |\n| `--lang <code>` | Output language (en, zh, ja, etc.) |\n| `--slides <number>` | Target slide count (8-25 recommended, max 30) |\n| `--outline-only` | Generate outline only, skip image generation |\n| `--prompts-only` | Generate outline + prompts, skip images |\n| `--images-only` | Generate images from existing prompts directory |\n| `--regenerate <N>` | Regenerate specific slide(s): `--regenerate 3` or `--regenerate 2,5,8` |\n\n**Slide Count by Content Length**:\n| Content | Slides |\n|---------|--------|\n| < 1000 words | 5-10 |\n\n[654 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773150622652}}
{"type":"message","id":"c59ac5f5","parentId":"726febd1","timestamp":"2026-03-10T13:50:37.196Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see! baoyu-slide-deck can generate slides from content. It uses the outline to generate prompts and then generates images. Let me see how to use it with the live script content.\n\nThe skill uses:\n- `--style` for visual style\n- `--audience` for target audience  \n- `--slides` for number of slides\n- `--outline-only` to generate outline only\n- `--prompts-only` to generate prompts only\n- `--images-only` to generate images from existing prompts\n- etc.\n\nLet me try using baoyu-slide-deck to generate the PPT. First, I need to prepare the content file (the live script), then run the command.\n\nBut wait, the user already has the PPT images generated. And baoyu-slide-deck would generate new images from scratch. So maybe the user wants a different STYLE of PPT using baoyu-slide-deck?\n\nLet me explain to the user and offer to generate a new version using baoyu-slide-deck with a different style.","thinkingSignature":"0157245e941b040565cf1bb5de3b6bbc55660bfe51e004032b11a05d4c5de42f"},{"type":"text","text":"收到苏神！可以的！\n\n---\n\n## 📋 baoyu-slide-deck 技能说明\n\n**用法**：\n```bash\n/baoyu-slide-deck path/to/content.md --style <风格> --slides 16 --lang zh\n```\n\n**风格选项**：\n- `sketch-notes`（素描笔记）\n- `corporate`（企业风格）\n- `minimalist`（极简）\n- 等等...\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 能不能用 baoyu-slide-deck 生成？\n\n当然可以！本王可以用 baoyu-slide-deck 重新生成一版！\n\n**只需要你告诉本王**：\n1. 用什么风格？（比如 corporate、minimalist、sketch-notes 等）\n2. 用哪个内容？（用今天直播的完整稿子？）\n\n苏神你想用 baoyu-slide-deck 生成什么风格的版本？🦐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":132863,"output":393,"cacheRead":41416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":174672,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773150622660}}
