{"type":"message","id":"220f95fc","parentId":"63c25447","timestamp":"2026-03-10T13:56:09.263Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说\"根据这个内容\"，意思是让我根据飞书文档的内容来选择风格。文档内容是关于直播的，主题是\"从“会聊”到“会干活”：虾王的技能落地全链路拆解\"。这是一个方法论+案例分享的直播内容。\n\n风格应该选择：\n- 专业、清晰、易懂\n- 适合教学/分享的风格\n\n让我用 baoyu-slide-deck 来生成，风格选一个适合这种直播分享的，比如 corporate 或 minimalist。\n\n模型用 Google 的。\n\n让我先读取直播稿内容，然后用 baoyu-slide-deck 生成。","thinkingSignature":"f37e5a2fd9157503543a30057d06642f785cef3c6820567047ec8d6700bee2f6"},{"type":"text","text":"收到苏神！好的！本王这就根据飞书文档内容，用 baoyu-slide-deck 生成一版 PPT！风格根据内容选择（直播分享+方法论），模型用 Google！\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9cl3bd5h4hg6_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/next-live-script.md","limit":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":52,"output":211,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":175229,"totalTokens":175492,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773150954167}}
{"type":"message","id":"d1cb60ec","parentId":"220f95fc","timestamp":"2026-03-10T13:56:09.281Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9cl3bd5h4hg6_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n&lt;callout emoji=\"shrimp\" background-color=\"light-blue\" border-color=\"light-blue\"&gt;\n这是一份可直接用于公开直播的长版逐字稿，主题为：**从“会聊”到“会干活”：虾王的技能落地全链路拆解**。\n整体定位：承接昨天的“翻车修复方法论”，讲“怎么给AI搭子做能力扩展”，形成完整上下篇。\n&lt;/callout&gt;\n\n---\n\n## 第一部分：开场回顾（建议 5-8 分钟）\n\n大家好，我是苏神。\n\n昨天我们讲了一个非常真实的主题：**苏神和虾王，那些一起翻过的车，最后都怎么修好了**。\n\n我们讲了七个翻车案例：\n- 发消息身份搞错了\n- 群聊规则没收住\n- 心跳规则只做了半套\n- 飞书语音明明生成了音频，却不是语音条\n- 安全基线报错，看起来像事故，其实是路径配置坑\n- 配置记忆改了，但系统配置没改\n- 双插件冲突，不是不能用，而是会一直埋暗雷\n\n然后我们提炼出了五个闭环：\n- 指令闭环\n- 记忆闭环\n- 执行闭环\n- 规则闭环\n- 反馈闭环\n\n最后我们说：\n&gt; AI 搭子真正的成熟，不是从不翻车，而是每翻一次车，都会比上一次更难再翻同样的车。\n\n今天，我们继续讲。\n\n昨天我们解决的是：**“AI 会犯错，怎么修”**。\n\n今天我们要解决的是：**“我怎么让我的 AI，从只会聊天，变成会真的帮我干活？”**\n\n这个问题我觉得更重要。\n\n因为很多人现在用 AI，都是停留在“聊”的阶段：\n- 聊个天\n- 问个问题\n- 让它写个文案\n- 让它出个主意\n\n但真正能落地到“干活”的，其实不多。\n\n比如：\n\n[443 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773150969275}}
{"type":"message","id":"ff36d174","parentId":"d1cb60ec","timestamp":"2026-03-10T13:56:17.664Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，内容是关于直播分享的，主题是\"从“会聊”到“会干活”\"，是方法论+案例分享的形式。这种内容适合用：\n- **corporate** 风格（专业企业风格，适合教学分享）\n- 或者 **minimalist**（简洁风格）\n\n让我用 baoyu-slide-deck 来生成。风格选 corporate，模型用 Google。\n\n让我先检查一下 baoyu-slide-deck 的脚本位置，然后运行。","thinkingSignature":"3e83a55e43bded8d2e18a9ba1ba40787ed987a40970d9494c55006eff3b3c8c3"},{"type":"text","text":"收到苏神！好的！本王这就根据直播稿内容，用 baoyu-slide-deck 生成一版！\n\n内容是直播分享+方法论，风格选 **corporate**（专业企业风格，适合教学分享），模型用 **Google**！\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_brjelqjnq9f5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace && ls -la skills/baoyu-slide-deck/scripts/","workdir":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":134476,"output":217,"cacheRead":41416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":176109,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773150969282}}
{"type":"message","id":"b25e5b16","parentId":"ff36d174","timestamp":"2026-03-10T13:56:17.698Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_brjelqjnq9f5_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"total 16\ndrwx------   4 suchuanlei  staff   128  3月  7 10:46 .\ndrwx------  12 suchuanlei  staff   384  3月  7 17:06 ..\n-rw-------   1 suchuanlei  staff  3167  3月  7 10:46 merge-to-pdf.ts\n-rw-------   1 suchuanlei  staff  3918  3月  7 10:46 merge-to-pptx.ts"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":14,"aggregated":"total 16\ndrwx------   4 suchuanlei  staff   128  3月  7 10:46 .\ndrwx------  12 suchuanlei  staff   384  3月  7 17:06 ..\n-rw-------   1 suchuanlei  staff  3167  3月  7 10:46 merge-to-pdf.ts\n-rw-------   1 suchuanlei  staff  3918  3月  7 10:46 merge-to-pptx.ts","cwd":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773150977690}}
{"type":"message","id":"98a25fb8","parentId":"b25e5b16","timestamp":"2026-03-10T13:56:43.811Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，baoyu-slide-deck 技能目录里有 merge-to-pptx.ts 脚本。但这个技能的使用方式好像不是直接用命令行，而是通过读取内容然后生成 PPT。让我看看 baoyu-slide-deck 的使用方式。","thinkingSignature":"230d5306457d5844388f72b3ee374fe6dc976a8ebe6db65928392c84a9830060"},{"type":"text","text":"收到苏神！本王看看 baoyu-slide-deck 怎么用！\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6w3bqkj9weep_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-slide-deck/SKILL.md","limit":100,"offset":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":134829,"output":136,"cacheRead":41416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":176381,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773150977698}}
{"type":"message","id":"da0742ab","parentId":"98a25fb8","timestamp":"2026-03-10T13:56:43.834Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6w3bqkj9weep_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"| < 1000 words | 5-10 |\n| 1000-3000 words | 10-18 |\n| 3000-5000 words | 15-25 |\n| > 5000 words | 20-30 (consider splitting) |\n\n## Style System\n\n### Presets\n\n| Preset | Dimensions | Best For |\n|--------|------------|----------|\n| `blueprint` (Default) | grid + cool + technical + balanced | Architecture, system design |\n| `chalkboard` | organic + warm + handwritten + balanced | Education, tutorials |\n| `corporate` | clean + professional + geometric + balanced | Investor decks, proposals |\n| `minimal` | clean + neutral + geometric + minimal | Executive briefings |\n| `sketch-notes` | organic + warm + handwritten + balanced | Educational, tutorials |\n| `watercolor` | organic + warm + humanist + minimal | Lifestyle, wellness |\n| `dark-atmospheric` | clean + dark + editorial + balanced | Entertainment, gaming |\n| `notion` | clean + neutral + geometric + dense | Product demos, SaaS |\n| `bold-editorial` | clean + vibrant + editorial + balanced | Product launches, keynotes |\n| `editorial-infographic` | clean + cool + editorial + dense | Tech explainers, research |\n| `fantasy-animation` | organic + vibrant + handwritten + minimal | Educational storytelling |\n| `intuition-machine` | clean + cool + technical + dense | Technical docs, academic |\n| `pixel-art` | pixel + vibrant + technical + balanced | Gaming, developer talks |\n| `scientific` | clean + cool + technical + dense | Biology, chemistry, medical |\n| `vector-illustration` | clean + vibrant + humanist + balanced | Creative, children's content |\n| `vintage` | paper + warm + editorial + balanced | Historical, heritage |\n\n### Style Dimensions\n\n| Dimension | Options | Description |\n|-----------|---------|-------------|\n| **Texture** | clean, grid, organic, pixel, paper | Visual texture and background treatment |\n| **Mood** | professional, warm, cool, vibrant, dark, neutral | Color temperature and palette style |\n| **Typography** | geometric, humanist, handwritten, editorial, technical | Headline and body text styling |\n| **Density** | minimal, balanced, dense | Information density per slide |\n\nFull specs: `references/dimensions/*.md`\n\n### Auto Style Selection\n\n| Content Signals | Preset |\n|-----------------|--------|\n| tutorial, learn, education, guide, beginner | `sketch-notes` |\n| classroom, teaching, school, chalkboard | `chalkboard` |\n| architecture, system, data, analysis, technical | `blueprint` |\n| creative, children, kids, cute | `vector-illustration` |\n| briefing, academic, research, bilingual | `intuition-machine` |\n| executive, minimal, clean, simple | `minimal` |\n| saas, product, dashboard, metrics | `notion` |\n| investor, quarterly, business, corporate | `corporate` |\n| launch, marketing, keynote, magazine | `bold-editorial` |\n| entertainment, music, gaming, atmospheric | `dark-atmospheric` |\n| explainer, journalism, science communication | `editorial-infographic` |\n| story, fantasy, animation, magical | `fantasy-animation` |\n| gaming, retro, pixel, developer | `pixel-art` |\n| biology, chemistry, medical, scientific | `scientific` |\n| history, heritage, vintage, expedition | `vintage` |\n| lifestyle, wellness, travel, artistic | `watercolor` |\n| Default | `blueprint` |\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nDecks designed for **reading and sharing**, not live presentation:\n- Each slide self-explanatory without verbal commentary\n- Logical flow when scrolling\n- All necessary context within each slide\n- Optimized for social media sharing\n\nSee `references/design-guidelines.md` for:\n- Audience-specific principles\n- Visual hierarchy\n- Content density guidelines\n- Color and typography selection\n- Font recommendations\n\nSee `references/layouts.md` for layout options.\n\n## File Management\n\n### Output Directory\n\n```\nslide-deck/{topic-slug}/\n├── source-{slug}.{ext}\n├── outline.md\n├── prompts/\n│   └── 01-slide-cover.md, 02-slide-{slug}.md, ...\n├── 01-slide-cover.png, 02-slide-{slug}.png, ...\n├── {topic-slug}.pptx\n└── {topic-slug}.pdf\n```\n\n**Slug**: Extract topic (2-4 words, kebab-case). Example: \"Introduction to Machine Learning\" → `intro-machine-learning`\n\n**Conflict Handling**: See Step 1.3 for existing content detection and user options.\n\n## Language Handling\n\n**Detection Priority**:\n\n[555 more lines in file. Use offset=150 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773151003825}}
