{"type":"message","id":"54d85251","parentId":"32eac61a","timestamp":"2026-03-10T14:01:35.743Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要把今晚做PPT的重要经验记录到 memory/2026-03-10.md 里！主要是：\n\n1. baoyu-slide-deck 技能的使用方式：\n   - 用法：`~/.bun/bin/bun ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-slide-deck/scripts/merge-to-pptx.ts <图片文件夹路径>`\n   - 会自动把文件夹里的图片按文件名排序合并成 PPT\n   - 输出文件名默认是 {文件夹名}.pptx\n\n2. 飞书文件发送限制：超过一定大小就会失败（400错误），只能发链接\n\n3. Google 模型生成PPT图片的配置和效果\n\n让我读取当前的 memory 文件然后追加新内容。","thinkingSignature":"c649db2fd2278d7aa11e4d5e3d0b9d1a2b656ebf2a3b42b49cb5af92d209abdc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0igga23ytl7z_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-10.md","old_string":"---\n\n_本王今天真的长记性了！下次发文件绝对不会再忘！🦐_","newText":"---\n\n## 📌 晚间补充：baoyu-slide-deck 技能使用\n\n### 任务复盘（2026-03-10 21:55-22:00）\n- **需求**：苏神问能不能用 baoyu-slide-deck 生成一版 PPT\n- **完成时间**：5分钟搞定\n- **结果**：成功！用 baoyu-slide-deck 的 merge-to-pptx.ts 脚本把16张图片合并成 .pptx\n\n### baoyu-slide-deck 正确用法\n```bash\n~/.bun/bin/bun ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-slide-deck/scripts/merge-to-pptx.ts <图片文件夹路径>\n```\n\n**例如**：\n```bash\n~/.bun/bin/bun ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-slide-deck/scripts/merge-to-pptx.ts /Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/next-live/images-google/\n```\n\n**效果**：\n- 自动扫描文件夹里的所有图片（按文件名排序）\n- 自动合并成 .pptx 文件\n- 输出文件位置：{图片文件夹路径}/{文件夹名}.pptx\n\n### 飞书文件发送限制\n- **问题**：飞书文件上传有大小限制（400错误）\n- **现象**：.pptx 文件超过一定大小（~20MB）就会发送失败\n- **解决方案**：只能告诉苏神本地路径，让他自己打开\n\n### 完整交付（三个版本 PPT）\n1. **DashScope 版**（python-pptx合并）\n2. **Google 版**（python-pptx合并）\n3. **Google 版-baoyu-slide-deck**（用 baoyu-slide-deck 脚本合并）\n\n---\n\n_本王今天真的长记性了！下次发文件绝对不会再忘！🦐_"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":52,"output":615,"cacheRead":23678,"cacheWrite":54205,"totalTokens":78550,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timest