_modules/@types/node/https.d.ts:     *   hostname: 'encrypted.google.com',\nskills/baoyu-slide-deck/node_modules/@types/node/https.d.ts:     * https.get('https://encrypted.google.com/', (res) => {\nskills/baoyu-slide-deck/node_modules/string_decoder/README.md:* Assisting in the implementation of stream providers within Node.js.\nskills/baoyu-slide-deck/node_modules/typescript/lib/lib.dom.d.ts: * The **`MediaKeySystemAccess`** interface of the Encrypted Media Extensions API provides access to a Key System for decryption and/or a content protection provider.\nskills/baoyu-slide-deck/node_modules/typescript/lib/lib.dom.d.ts:     * The **`login`** read-only property of the Navigator interface provides access to the browser's NavigatorLogin object, which a federated identity provider (IdP) can use to set its login status when a user signs into or out of the IdP.\nskills/baoyu-slide-deck/node_modules/typescript/lib/lib.dom.d.ts: * The **`NavigatorLogin`** interface of the Federated Credential Management (FedCM) API defines login functionality for federated identity providers (IdPs).\nskills/baoyu-slide-deck/node_modules/typescript/lib/lib.dom.d.ts:     * The **`setStatus()`** method of the NavigatorLogin interface sets the login status of a federated identity provider (IdP), when called from the IdP's origin.\nskills/baoyu-slide-deck/node_modules/typescript/lib/lib.dom.d.ts:     * The `external` property of the Window API returns an instance of the `External` interface, which was intended to contain functions related to adding external search providers to the browser.\nskills/baoyu-slide-deck/node_modules/typescript/lib/lib.dom.d.ts: * The `external` property of the Window API returns an instance of the `External` interface, which was intended to contain functions related to adding external search providers to the browser."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":323,"aggregated":"skills/baoyu-slide-deck/node_modules/pako/README.md:  [Tedit](https://ch