{"type":"message","id":"d6a447b9","parentId":"bbd1c85e","timestamp":"2026-03-10T15:10:06.764Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完美！苏神！压缩版 PPT 成功发送了！🎉\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 交付完成！\n\n**压缩版 PPT** 已成功发送到飞书！\n\n---\n\n## 📦 完整交付（四个版本）\n\n1. **DashScope 版**：`/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/next-live/从会聊到会干活-DashScope版.pptx`\n2. **Google 版**：`/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/next-live/从会聊到会干活-Google版.pptx`\n3. **baoyu-slide-deck 版**（PNG）：`/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/从会聊到会干活/从会聊到会干活.pptx`\n4. **baoyu-slide-deck 压缩版**（JPG，已发送）：已发送到飞书！\n\n---\n\n苏神你查收一下！🦐✨"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773155394995}}
