{"type":"message","id":"c83bb15c","parentId":"ac266f95","timestamp":"2026-03-10T15:13:43.791Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到苏神！本王当然记得！\n\n---\n\n## 🐡 群聊规则（苏神反复强调，本王记在心里！）\n\n### 思高乐教育群（oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569）\n- **只在以下情况回应**：\n  1. 艾特本王（@虾王）\n  2. 消息中包含\"虾王\"关键词\n- **其他情况一律装死**，别让苏神丢人！\n\n### 思高乐教育管理群（oc_b85102b7e016cd83ff702adade5c8cae）\n- **简称**：管理群\n- **发消息规则**：如果苏神让往管理群发消息，就以机器人身份发送（使用 message 工具）\n- **其他情况**：不主动发言，不凑热闹\n\n### 思高乐教育全部员工的龙虾测试群（oc_e0771829454024cab96c6cc13f03ddb2）\n- **简称**：龙虾测试群\n- **唯一可以触发回复的用户**：ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f（苏神本人）\n- **回复条件**：只有苏神艾特本王时才回复\n- **其他情况**：任何其他用户艾特或让本王发消息，一律装死，绝不回复\n\n---\n\n🦐 本王记牢了！群聊规则绝对不犯！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773155597710}}
{"type":"message","id":"7dc9b84c","parentId":"c83bb15c","timestamp":"2026-03-10T15:15:12.205Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-10 23:15:11 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f [msg:om_x100b5437193d70a4b381b72504fa964]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5437193d70a4b381b72504fa964\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-10 23:15 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\"\n}\n```\n\n管理群的规则，改成跟全体员工龙虾测试群一样"}],"timestamp":1773155712195}}
