{"type":"message","id":"2d32ad0d","parentId":"f07b6fb7","timestamp":"2026-03-10T15:34:04.461Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到苏神！公众号推文已写好！现在本王开始用 baoyu-slide-deck 做 PPT！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_xqw8yqq0jh1zezhr3igoedbn","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/2026-03-10-公众号PPT/outline.md","content":"# 从\"会聊\"到\"会干活\"：虾王的三个真实案例\n\n## 大纲\n\n| # | 标题 | 类型 | 布局 |\n|---|------|------|------|\n| 1 | 封面 | 封面 | title-hero |\n| 2 | 昨天我们讲了什么 | 内容 | text-heavy |\n| 3 | 今天我们要解决 | 内容 | text-heavy |\n| 4 | 能力落地的五个闭环 | 内容 | text-heavy |\n| 5 | 闭环一：需求闭环 | 内容 | text-heavy |\n| 6 | 闭环二：技能闭环 | 内容 | text-heavy |\n| 7 | 闭环三：记忆闭环 | 内容 | text-heavy |\n| 8 | 闭环四：执行闭环 | 内容 | text-heavy |\n| 9 | 闭环五：纠错闭环 | 内容 | text-heavy |\n| 10 | 案例一：Get笔记 | 内容 | text-heavy |\n| 11 | 案例二：语音克隆 | 内容 | text-heavy |\n| 12 | 案例三：公众号发布 | 内容 | text-heavy |\n| 13 | 总结：能力落地的五个关键 | 内容 | text-heavy |\n| 14 | 结尾升华 | 内容 | hero |\n| 15 | 谢谢大家 | 结束页 | hero |\n\n## 风格配置\n\n- **Preset**: corporate\n- **Dimensions**: clean + professional + geometric + balanced\n- **Audience**: General readers\n- **Language**: zh\n\n## 输出目录\n\n`/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/2026-03-10-公众号PPT/`\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773156817739}}
